          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍孤看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平贵无道，平贵无道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦呵呀！看这宾鸿大雁，骂孤无道，此乃不祥之兆。\n内侍，看弓弹伺候。"
