    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "代战公主",
        "番官",
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（番官、小番同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了公主命，把守在头关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩子们带路上关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，开关！"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了公主将令，出关另有公干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有公主将令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩子们开关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵过关，下。代战公主、马达、江海、四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见公主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，我且问你，可见大王爷过关无有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "番官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人有一个过关，不知可是大王？"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你连大王爷都不认识，来，与我打！兵发二关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
