    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "代战公主",
        "江海",
        "莫老将军",
        "薛平贵",
        "马达"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、莫老将军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白盔白甲白旗号，白胡白须白眉毛。白吃白喝白眺眼，白打白闹白扯搔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，莫老将军是也。奉主旨意，镇守三关。儿郎带路上关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫老将军、四青袍同上关。薛平贵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，来此吾国地界，隔界三关。看城上好相莫老将军模样，待我来冒叫一声。\n吓，城上莫老将军请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了请了，何人叫老夫名讳？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先行平贵回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打鬼打鬼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何言“打鬼”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你死在西凉夏国，跑到我这里显魂来呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仇人甚多，咒骂于我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有何为证？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红鬃烈马为证。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套内同喊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，老将军，后面追兵甚急，快快开城再叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我谅你一人，也反不到哪里去。\n来，开城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵进城，下。代战公主、马达、江海、四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启公主：来此他国三关，"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，到了三关？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达、江海",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去叫关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马达、江海同允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来，到了他国地面，说话要和气点。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达、江海",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n老头请呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老头不玩火球。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老姜到菜市买去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大黄药店买去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肘子要到肉店里买去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鱼摊上买。你们两个人，长的人不人鬼不鬼，也配长了两条仙鹤腿。找一个好\n面孔的来说罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马达、江海",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请公主上前答话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待我向前。\n城上的老伯将军请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "城下小老太太请了！到此间事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "借问老将军，先行平贵、我国大王过去无有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你国大王没有看见，我国先行平贵回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军有所不知：你国先行平贵，就是我国大王。他若过关，烦你老人家，请\n他上城来，我们说上三言两句，即刻带兵回去。也不招灾，也不惹祸，老将军，\n你说好是不好呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫头吓，丫头！我国先行平贵，精精壮壮，被你们掠了去，不教他好事，尽教\n他吃鸦片烟，弄的面孔饥瘦。我这里有钩镰枪，把你钩上来，把你浑身衣服剥\n掉，看看你是男是女。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这老小子真不是东西！\n马达、江海攻城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马达、江海同允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，慢来，你一个顶明白的人，同我这么一个老头子斗什么？你将人马暂退\n一箭之地，我把先行平贵请上城楼，你们两人爱唱什么唱什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须要言而有信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫老将军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂肯失信与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "代战公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，将人马暂退一箭之地。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（代战公主、马达、江海、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
